data.description: ATTENTION VA BUYERS: Call to find out how you can assume the seller's 3.75% interest rate. Welcome home to Marbella! This 2022 townhome is uniquely laid out to make the most of bright open-concept living. Modern essential features include a kitchen island that flows into the living room, stainless steel appliances, ceramic tile flooring, paver driveway, and a Smart Home System! The new homeowners will also enjoy family-friendly amenities; a community club house, swimming pool, lake, observation deck and walking path. Marbella is within proximity to Florida Keys Outlet Marketplace, Florida’s Turnpike, local farmer markets, tasty restaurants and the beautiful Florida Keys! No CDDs. Schedule your tour today, so you can love where you live at Marbella!!
